query_1_sql: SELECT la.timestamp, la.status, la.ip_address, la.device_id FROM login_attempts la WHERE la.user_id = 'U008' AND la.timestamp < '2025-07-07 14:48:10' ORDER BY la.timestamp DESC LIMIT 5;
query_2_sql: SELECT t.timestamp, t.amount, t.location, t.device_id, t.ip_address FROM transactions t WHERE t.user_id = 'U008' AND t.timestamp BETWEEN '2025-07-01' AND '2025-07-07 14:48:10' ORDER BY t.timestamp DESC;

query_3_sql: SELECT a.alert_id, a.alert_type, a.timestamp, a.description FROM alerts a WHERE a.user_id = 'U008' AND a.timestamp BETWEEN '2025-06-01' AND '2025-07-07 14:48:10' ORDER BY a.timestamp DESC;
query_4_sql: SELECT d.device_id, d.device_type, d.os, d.last_seen_ip FROM devices d JOIN user_devices ud ON d.device_id = ud.device_id WHERE ud.user_id = 'U008' AND d.last_seen_ip IN (SELECT la.ip_address FROM login_attempts la WHERE la.user_id = 'U008' AND la.status = 'failed');
query_5_sql: SELECT p.payee_id, p.payee_name, p.email, p.phone_number FROM payees p JOIN user_payees up ON p.payee_id = up.payee_id WHERE up.user_id = 'U008' AND p.registered_location != 'Singapore';
query_6_sql: SELECT COUNT(*) as failed_count FROM login_attempts WHERE user_id = 'U008' AND status = 'failed' AND timestamp > datetime('now', '-24 hours')
query_8_sql: SELECT * FROM transactions WHERE user_id = 'U008' ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
query_9_sql: SELECT * FROM login_attempts WHERE user_id = 'U008' ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
query_11_sql: SELECT d.* FROM devices d JOIN user_devices ud ON d.device_id = ud.device_id WHERE ud.user_id = 'U008';
